## Key Daggerheart Mechanics Referenced

### Hope and Fear System
- **Hope Die**: Player resource die
- **Fear Die**: GM resource die
- Hope/Fear tokens are spent to activate abilities

### Damage and Thresholds
- **Minor/Major/Severe Thresholds**: Damage breakpoints
- **HP**: Hit Points for adversaries/segments
- **Stress**: Mental/emotional damage resource

### Combat Ranges
- Melee
- Very Close
- Close
- Far
- Very Far

### Damage Types
- **phy** (physical)
- **mag** (magical)

### Equipment Features
- **Versatile**: Can use with alternate stats
- **Powerful**: Roll extra damage die, drop lowest
- **Paired**: Bonus damage with primary weapon
- **Protective/Barrier**: Armor Score bonuses
- **Heavy/Very Heavy**: Evasion penalties

